### Motivation and context

Bootstrap 5.3 introduced a dark mode, which works by setting the `data-bs-theme=dark` attribute.  However, this theme does not look good when printing, because the browser trys to convert it to a light theme. So being able to have the light theme only during print would be much appreciated.
For example:
```css
@media print {
    $bootstrap-theme="light";
}
```

